.IX Subsection "DESCRIPTION"
This class extends the Search::Elasticsearch client with a \f(CW\*(C`graph\*(C'\fR
namespace, to support the \s-1API\s0 for the
Graph <https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/x-pack/current/xpack-graph.html> plugin for Elasticsearch.
.SH "METHODS"
.IX Header "METHODS"
