.IX Subsection "explore()"
.Vb 5
\&    $response = $es\->graph\->explore(
\&        index => $index | \e@indices,        # optional
\&        type  => $type  | \e@types,          # optional
\&        body  => {...}
\&    )
.Ve
.PP
The \f(CW\*(C`explore()\*(C'\fR method allows you to discover vertices and connections which relate
to your query.
.PP
See the explore docs <https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/graph-explore-api.html>
for more information.
.PP
